k admitted she did not know what Collins meant but said she would not argue.\", \"from\": 1432, \"to\": 1549, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1506, \"end\": 1513, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HarperCollins\", \"score\": 0.743268853616315, \"rank\": 0.34540818441678567, \"text\": \"Collins\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HarperCollins\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HarperCollins\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"More than three months later, the 30-year-old has now addressed their disagreement and admitted she could have taken a \\\"different approach\\\".\", \"from\": 1550, \"to\": 1690, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think what happened on the court is very much just like sometimes people have friction at work,\\\" the formerAustralian Openfinalist toldThe Athletic.\", \"from\": 1692, \"to\": 1843, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"For most people, it's not on the news.\", \"from\": 1844, \"to\": 1883, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am trying to be the best person that I can be, but that's not to say that I do not fall short of that.\", \"from\": 1885, \"to\": 1990, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I could have taken a different approach and done some things differently.\", \"from\": 1991, \"to\": 2064, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But we had a moment there on court.\\\"\", \"from\": 2065, \"to\": 2101, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But the two tennis stars still have not properly spoken since.\", \"from\": 2103, \"to\": 2165, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She's not someone that I really get to see a lot at the tennis and she's very guarded with her group,\\\" Collins added.\", \"from\": 2166, \"to\": 2284, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2270, \"end\": 2277, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HarperCollins\", \"score\": 0.743268853616315, \"rank\": 0.34540818441678567, \"text\": \"Collins\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24